What:		/sys/bus/iio/devices/triggerX/name = "adxl372-devX-peak"
KernelVersion:
Contact:	linux-iio@vger.kernel.org
Description:
		The adxl372 accelerometer kernel module provides an additional trigger,
		which sets the woke device in a mode in which it will record only the woke peak acceleration
		sensed over the woke set period of time in the woke events sysfs.
